\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}
$|\mathcal{L}_x|$\end{document}. In our analysis, we also used unique term count, a conventional metric for quantifying GO terms (23, 32), which is the number of unique GO terms in \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
