Following Clark et al, we model the relationships between GO terms in the ontology using a Bayesian network and thus assume each GO term is independent of its ancestors, given its parents (39). Under this assumption, the probability of any protein being annotated with a sub-graph T of the ontology, denoted as \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
